{{Infobox website |name = College Football News |logo = |logocaption = |screenshot = College Football News homepage.PNG |screenshot_size = 250px |collapsible = |collapsetext = |caption = |url = {{URL|http://www.collegefootballnews.com/}} |slogan = |commercial = Yes |type = [[Online magazine]] |registration = |language = [[English language|English]] |content license = |owner = |author = |launch date = |alexa = |revenue = |current status = }} '''''College Football News''''' ('''''CFN''''') is a magazine and website published by College Football News, Inc., headquartered in [[Chicago, Illinois]]. News coverage includes scores, statistics, rankings, and reports on [[college football]] games. Analysis includes comparisons between teams, predictions of game outcomes and high-school recruiting information. They also give awards to players in various categories.{{ref|MBTF}}{{ref|SU}}
