![[LPGA|LPGA Tour]]
| [[Golf]] || {{flagicon|USA}}<ref group=nb name=LPGA>Most LPGA events are held in the US, but it also sole-sanctions official money events in Thailand, Singapore, Mexico, China, Canada, Malaysia, and Taiwan, as well as an unofficial event in Brazil. Since 2013, two of its [[women's major golf championships|majors]], [[Women's British Open|one]] in the UK and [[The Evian Championship|the other]] in France, have been co-sanctioned with the [[Ladies European Tour]]. The LPGA also co-sanctions events with the [[LPGA of Korea Tour|Korean LPGA]] and [[LPGA of Japan Tour|Japan LPGA]] in those countries and the [[ALPG Tour]] in Australia.</ref>
